9. House:gothic-revival is on the far left
10. Flower:azalea is on the left or right of Game:poker
11. Game:canastas is on the left or right of Flower:rose
12. Flower:lily == Music-Genre:pop
13. House:colonial == Flower:marigold
14. House:gothic-revival is on the left or right of Food:corn
15. Flower:azalea is on the left or right of Music-Genre:r&b

